parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger seat power adjustment module can cause a no-start condition, potentially leaving the driver and passengers stranded, and also compromise the proper functioning of the airbag system and child seat installation.

inability to obtain proper clearance from the airbag
inability to properly adjust the seat for child seat installation.
